You can access the project by putting all the files in the respository in a folder named "bookstore"
Open XAMPP
Start Apache and MySQL
Open your browser
Type in the URL : localhost/phpmyadmin
Create a New Database and name it "bookstore"
Get the contents in database.sql file and copy them (OR you can create the database manually)
Paste in SQL in phpMyAdmin and press Go
Put the bookstore folder in xampp in htdocs
Open your browser
Type in the URL : localhost/bookstore/index.php
